			<description><![CDATA[<p>
Were looking for talented, passionate Software Engineers to come and help build and maintain FreeAgent, our hugely popular flagship product. You&#39;ll have a deep interest in high-volume web appications and how to scale them, and you&#39;ll thrive in developing creative solutions to solve complex technical challenges using your Computer Science background.</p>
<p>
<strong>Required</strong></p>
<p>
&nbsp;</p>
<ul>
<li>
Minimum of 3 years experience in programming web apps, ideally using Ruby on Rails and ideally in a commercial environment</li>
<li>
Thorough understanding of OOD, TDD and MVC</li>
<li>
Ability to quickly solve problems and make pragmatic engineering decisions</li>
<li>
MySQL experience, the deeper knowledge you have the better</li>
<li>
Pro-active, &#39;can do&#39; attitude</li>
<li>
BSc/Masters degree in Computer Science or equivalent</li>
</ul>
<p>
<strong>Desired</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>
Previous experience working on high-traffic commercial web applications, ideally in SaaS</li>
<li>
Open source contributions</li>
</ul>
<p>
We&#39;re looking for people to work full-time with the team in our lovely Edinburgh office, but we will consider a remote working arrangement for exceptional candidates. We have a relocation package available and Edinburgh is a fantastic place to live!</p>
<p>
Youll get to work in our fantastic office in central Edinburgh with some of the best Rubyists in the UK. We provide weekly catered team lunches, free fruit and drinks, free beer fridge, Aeron chairs and you&#39;ll get to use the best hardware we can find.</p>
<p>
Tell us about yourself, we&#39;re interested!</p>
